Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:42.19,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,年刊  关东煮的东方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那从最低的奖开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,七等奖  最后一位是5
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,六等奖  最后两位是42
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,五等奖  最后三位是592
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四等奖  52331
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三等奖  244953
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  还剩两个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二等奖  89336122
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一等奖  19640627
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…我是在想一等奖的号码和我妈妈的生日一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太容易混淆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  果然是没中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过稍微有些紧张还是很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是「早起只有零日圆的好处」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第28届青空食品摄影大赛特别奖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,岸 麻衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:50.06,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（画面上出现的就是她嘴里念的，只是最底下一行“作品名”她没念）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个岸女士是你们之前说的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:19:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,获奖作品名  里新宿之狼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶～～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃你帮我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我那儿的香波用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,岸学姐真的为了实现梦想而努力的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,付出就会有回报的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚能让我住你这儿么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有可能梦想会破灭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是在说油菜同学的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有这层意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会即使像岸学姐一样为着梦想而奋斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却由于自己能力不济的原因而致使梦想破灭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:20:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不放弃就一直存在于此处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我觉得油菜学姐也是只要没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想就会一直存续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄不好是扔了素描本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是如同岸学姐一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了自己真正想干的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  或许是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许那个人在不为我所知的地方正努力着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为着自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说啊  我问过岸学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问她我是不是也能找到梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想是不会逃到任何地方去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃的梦想也一定会在某处等待被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她在一直地等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多睡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得定好闹钟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  忘记买电池了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说明早也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  闹钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:10.79,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,9月4日  完  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙儿  校长他好过分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄得我都想哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.68,0:23:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学和平时不大一样的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.06,0:23:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是特殊的日子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都会变成一个和平常不同的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:23:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.15,0:24:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃午饭去吧  吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集是  「11月3日  由乃殿下」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在山吹高中等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要来看哦
